com.northconcepts.datapipeline.core

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.northconcepts.datapipeline.core.Node
      • com.northconcepts.datapipeline.core.Field
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Session, ValueNodeContainer, Serializable, Comparable<Field>

    public final class Field
extends Node
implements ValueNodeContainer, Comparable<Field>, Serializable
    Field holds persistent key-value data as part of a record. Values in a field can be:
    • Single values (boolean, date, string, etc. -- see FieldType)
    • Records
    • Array of single values, records, and arrays
      See Also:
      SingleValue, Record, ArrayValue, FieldType, Serialized Form
